"        <p><a href=\"https://www.royalsociety.org.nz/what-we-do/funds-and-"
"opportunities/catalyst-fund/catalyst-influence/\"><strong>Catalyst: "
"Influence</strong></a></p>\n"
"        <p>Supports New Zealand science sector participation in, and "
"membership of, key international science fora and targeted engagement that "
"cannot be supported through other means.</br>\n"
"          On behalf of the New Zealand research base, the Royal Society Te "
"Apārangi manages the country’s representation in more than forty "
"international scientific unions.\n"
"          This facilitates the sharing of New Zealand’s expertise worldwide "
"and helps enable the international exchange of ideas.</p>\n"
"        <p><a href=\"https://www.royalsociety.org.nz/what-we-do/funds-and-"
"opportunities/catalyst-fund/catalyst-leaders/\"><strong>Catalyst: Leaders</"
"strong></a></p>\n"
"        <p>Supports incoming and outgoing targeted international fellowships "
"for exceptional individuals that cannot be supported through other means.</"
"p>\n"
"        <p><a href=\"https://www.royalsociety.org.nz/what-we-do/funds-and-"
"opportunities/catalyst-fund/catalyst-seeding/\"><strong>Catalyst: Seeding</"
"strong></a></p>\n"
"        <p>Facilitates new small and medium pre-research strategic "
"partnerships that cannot be supported through other means, and with a view "
"to developing full collaborations that\n"
"          could be supported through Catalyst: Strategic over time.</p>\n"
"      "
msgstr ""

