#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:56
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Academic record is requested to enable analysis of the effect of "
"qualifications on research performance,\n"
"        career trajectories, and to better understand needs for succession "
"planning and support for particular groups.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"E tonoa ana he whakaaturanga mātauranga kia taea ai te tātari te pānga o ngā "
"tohu ki te whakatutukitanga rangahau, ngā rerenga ara mahi, ā, kia mārama "
"ake ai ki te mahere tauatanga me te tautoko i ētahi rōpū ake. \n"
"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:62
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Prizes and/or medals are requested in order to enable analysis over "
"time of the causes and effects of recognition.\n"
